CatDescriptText: From left to right in the front: Melvin Carb, Fred Foxx, Louis Zegarelli, Dolores Cyphers, Lee Bocchiachio, Marguerite Dodson, Val "Moke" Capone, Bob Doran, Fritzie "Freddy" Jones (Ahmad Jamal).  Back row: Catherine Moore, Jack Strong, Clyde Davidson, Carl McVicker (director), Gwendolyn Baylor, Richard Adams, Carl Robinson, William "Bud" Stark, and Jerry Elliot.  Also included is Conrad "Connie" Snyder.
TitMainTitle: Westinghouse High School swing band "The K-dets," from left in front: Melvin Carb, Fred Foxx, Louis Zegarelli, Dolores Cyphers, Lee Bocchiachio, Marguerite Dodson, Val "Moke" Capone, Bob Doran, Ahmad Jamal (formerly Fritz "Freddy" Jones); back row: Catherine Moore, Jack Strong, Clyde Davidson, director Carl McVicker, Gwendolyn Baylor, Richard Adams, Carl Robinson, William "Bud" Stark, and Jerry Elliot; also included is Conrad "Connie" Snyder
